snippet.title: MatchyGotchy Z™ - Virtual Pet - Steam PC - Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist MatchyGotchy Z™ Here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/888220/MatchyGotchy_Z/

MatchyGotchy Z™ is a colorful digital pet game that combines idle clicker elements with a new take on pet-raising simulation: trainable personalities. All the nostalgia of those old virtual pets, fully adapted into a new desktop gaming experience.
